{"tid":1503310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街司機","createTime":"2019-08-25T02:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T02:58:08.000Z","uid":286135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"17472a54986a5a117324981773608ea368d16d35","tid":1503310,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:43:18.000Z","msg":"非行動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3DTHei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3DTHei.jpg&h=342deba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我琴日係megabox外警察封既路前<br />\n指揮車輛掉頭同埋開路比緊急車輛<br />\n呢架車少說有12個碌<br />\n我企係馬路舉起雙手示意停車<br />\n雖然無加速但係未見有煞車<br />\n開頭以為煞車不及，然後我向右行讓出車路<br />\n點不知佢比油向左摟汰，我再向左後退<br />\n佢即刻向右摟太，我即刻掉頭跑<br />\n我講咁詳細既原因係為左證明司機非煞制不及<br />\n希望有師兄無論工作上或私底下識呢條友<br />\n可以多多小心佢，提防佢"},{"pid":"4118fd694a8da13ad32d3ae28405de6aafd95381","tid":1503310,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"有一刻以為自己要死啦"},{"pid":"fb7802b9e6964fe9d0f08e580a11edafa0589e7c","tid":1503310,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:43:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,未必CALL 到人, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月6 (六), 9 月7(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場</span>"},{"pid":"9c42c85dd826bf02be04eac04fbadd988911df21","tid":1503310,"uid":217452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:45:11.000Z","msg":"SM 3276 <br />\n俊和<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f31fee358a962b4e6ffa19f184b19d66158334","tid":1503310,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己差d死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f8d3775e8935ec55b8b13755323c60da40f79d","